  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (bounded operating envelope, clean)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5 within a fully declared and bounded operating envelope (flow rate 2–8 L/min; rotational speed 2000–4000 RPM; hematocrit 35–45%). Validation experiments cover all four boundary corners plus three interior operating points. All 13 credibility factors are assessed; achieved levels meet or exceed required levels at MRL 5. Decision: Accepted.",
